caption:
It’s always been a dream of mine to combine my love of pure running and professional triathlon.

My partnership with @HOKA allows me to do just that, and for my dreams to fly! 

HOKA has for a long time been at the forefront of both triathlon and running. It’s now my honor to be there with them.

In the lead up to LA28, you’ll see the pace we are progressing in both sports in pursuit of representing Team USA once more… starting this weekend in Houston.

#FlyHumanFly
#Hoka
